data.title: Size Shouldn't Mean Compromise
data.description: Bearwear is hoping to make the larger man feel good about how they look and make it easier for them to find what they like. We've spoken to some customers who have said they used to wear a 2XL even though they're a 3XL simply because they couldn't find their correct size in regular retail outlets. We're hoping to make this a thing of the past! Our clothes are modern and stylish and would not look out of place whether they were sized medium or 5XL.
